graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator<br/>v1.39.0]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    TrustyAI -->|service mesh| Istio[Istio]
    TrustyAI -->|certificate mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager]
    TrustyAI -->|job scheduling| Kueue[Kueue]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|watch/patch CRD| KServe[KServe InferenceService]
    TrustyAI -->|label detection| ModelMesh[Model Mesh]
    TrustyAI -->|platform config| DSC[Data Science Cluster ConfigMap]

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -.->|optional storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL Database]
    TrustyAI -.->|optional storage| MySQL[MySQL Database]
    TrustyAI -.->|telemetry| OTLP[OpenTelemetry Collector]

    %% Integration Points (Reverse Dependencies)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| TrustyAI
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto evaluation| TrustyAI

    %% Managed Components
    TrustyAI -->|creates/manages| TASService[TrustyAI Service<br/>Explainability]
    TrustyAI -->|creates/manages| LMESJobs[LM Evaluation Jobs<br/>Model Assessment]
    TrustyAI -->|creates/manages| GORCHService[Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>AI Safety]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    TASService -->|stores data| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]
    TASService -.->|or database| PostgreSQL
    TASService -.->|or database| MySQL
    TASService -->|exposes metrics| PrometheusOp

    GORCHService -->|calls detectors| KServe
    GORCHService -->|calls generators| KServe
    GORCHService -->|exports telemetry| OTLP

    LMESJobs -->|downloads models| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    LMESJobs -->|downloads datasets| HuggingFace[Dataset Repositories]
    LMESJobs -->|evaluates| KServe
    LMESJobs -.->|queued by| Kueue

    %% Istio Integration
    Istio -->|mTLS for| TASService
    Istio -->|mTLS for| GORCHService
    Istio -->|VirtualService| TASService

    %% OpenShift Integration
    OpenShift -->|exposes| TASService
    OpenShift -->|exposes| GORCHService

